    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 未改变恢复石油生产的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/opec-makes-no-changes-to-plans-for-reviving-oil-production</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管有迹象表明即将出现过剩局面，但 OPEC+ 并未改变年底前开始逐步恢复石油生产的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/opec-makes-no-changes-to-plans-for-reviving-oil-production</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 14:30:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙称欧洲监管过度、投资不足</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-02/macron-says-europe-is-over-regulating-under-investing-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙警告称，如果欧盟不提高与中国和美国的竞争力，它可能会灭亡。“我们监管过度，投资不足。在未来两到三年内，如果我们按照传统议程行事，我们将退出市场，”他在柏林全球对话由彭博社的斯蒂芬妮·弗兰德斯主持的小组讨论中说道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-02/macron-says-europe-is-over-regulating-under-investing-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 14:20:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BlueCrest 未能阻止向投资者支付 7 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/bluecrest-loses-court-bid-to-block-700-million-investor-payout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迈克尔·普拉特 (Michael Platt) 的投资公司 BlueCrest Capital Management 在与英国金融监管机构的诉讼中败诉后，再次面临向投资者赔偿 7 亿美元的义务，原因是该公司在内部基金中偏袒员工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/bluecrest-loses-court-bid-to-block-700-million-investor-payout</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:36:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国码头工人罢工：衡量经济成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-02/us-dockworker-s-strike-measuring-the-economic-cost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，美国东部和墨西哥湾沿岸各大港口的码头工人因未能就新合同达成一致而罢工，这是近 50 年来首次。彭博经济的 Anna Wong 在彭博电视台上分析了此次罢工对美国经济的潜在影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-02/us-dockworker-s-strike-measuring-the-economic-cost</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:28:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利央行在福林贬值后承诺实施“有限”绿色计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/hungarian-central-bank-pledges-limited-green-program-after-forint-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利央行承诺维持“严谨而紧缩”的货币政策，以缓解投资者的担忧，因为福林跌至一年半以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/hungarian-central-bank-pledges-limited-green-program-after-forint-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:08:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
